                            </div>

                            <div style="display: flex; gap: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                                <div style="flex: 1; text-align: center; background: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.1); padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px;">
                                    <div class="stat" style="font-size: 48px; margin: 0;">7.97s</div>
