                                </div>
                                <div style="flex: 1; text-align: center; background: rgba(232, 185, 35, 0.1); padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px;">
                                    <div class="stat" style="font-size: 48px; margin: 0;">$0.006</div>
                                    <p style="font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 0;">Cost per image</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <h3 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;">✅ 4 Knowledge Gaps Found</h3>
                            <div style="background: #FFF9E6; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #E8B923;">
                                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">• Simultaneous equations (solving systems)</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">• Linear equations (prerequisite skill)</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">• Fraction operations (foundational)</p>
                                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0; font-weight: 600;">• Arithmetic patterns (number sense)</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="caption" style="margin-top: 24px;">Live production system • Deployed March 15, 2026</p>
