                        <div style="text-align: left; max-width: 500px; margin: 20px auto; font-size: 14px;">
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">📱 <strong>WhatsApp API</strong> → Teacher uploads photo</p>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">☁️ <strong>AWS S3</strong> → Secure cloud storage</p>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">🤖 <strong>Claude AI (Haiku 4.5)</strong> → Analyzes against 27 curriculum nodes</p>
                            <p style="margin-left: 30px; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px;">• Identifies misconceptions</p>
                            <p style="margin-left: 30px; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px;">• Traces prerequisite gaps</p>
                            <p style="margin-left: 30px; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 15px;">• Detects error patterns</p>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">💾 <strong>PostgreSQL Database</strong> → Historical tracking</p>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">📊 <strong>Teacher Dashboard</strong> → WhatsApp report + web view</p>
                        </div>
                        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 25px;">✅ 27 curriculum nodes mapped (Ghana Primary Math)</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 14px;">✅ Multi-country ready (Uganda, Kenya, Nigeria)</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 14px;">✅ Production deployed (AWS ECS + RDS + Load Balancer)</p>
